STATE
v.
Henry Lee JAMES. No. 19P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 2, 2006. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, Frank R. Parrish, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 6th day of January 2006 by Defendant for "Writ of Discretionary Review":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 2nd day of March 2006."
